Package: speciesmap
Type: Package
Title: Species Occurrences And Climate Observations
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Remko Duursma, Daisy Duursma
Depends: ALA4R, rgbif, raster
Maintainer: Remko Duursma <remkoduursma@gmail.com>
Description: Retrieve species occurrences from GBIF or ALA, and retrieve climate variables at the occurrences from WorldClim. Optionally rasterize occurrences at resolution of Worldclim to reduce sampling bias.
License: GPL-2
